</p>
                 <h4>5. Significance:</h4>
                 <p>- Rasmi Badi is a beloved dish in Uttarakhand, often prepared during festivals, special occasions, or family gatherings.
   - The use of locally sourced lentils and the unique flavor from mustard oil make it a staple in the traditional cuisine of the region.
